      "content": "You should absolutely not stop taking your sertraline abruptly, or suddenly switch to St. John's Wort without a plan. Mixing or switching these substances can cause serious interactions, potentially leading to a dangerous condition called serotonin syndrome. You need to discuss a safe tapering schedule with your prescribing physician before making any changes to your medication regimen.",
